All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
AdminPanel
Description:
The AdminPanel class is responsible for constructing the panel that contains these administration tools: Ban Unban Kick Silence
Ban
Description:
Ban represents the ban command that is called if either an admin or the bot itself calls for a ban.
Bot
Description:
The "main" class that is responsible for initializing the bot, as well as housing any utility methods that fulfill common tasks for Discord, such as joining voice channels, or retrieving permissions for roles.
CommandObject
Description:
Abstract class that all commands are an extension of.
Config
Description:
The Config class is responsible for gathering all the necessary information used for starting and running the bot.
DevPanel
Description:
The DevPanel class is responsible for constructing the text box that displays any events or commands executed from any guild, or any dev message that would appear in the Java terminal.
EventObject
Description:
Abstract class that all events are an extension of.
GuiFrame
Description:
The GuiFrame class is the frame that contains the individual panels used in the GUI.
GuildPanel
Description:
The GuildPanel class is responsible for constructing the guild panel, which contains the list of guilds that the bot is currently present in.
GuiMain
Description:
The "main" class responsible for initializing the GUI.
Handler
Description:
The Handler class is responsible for parsing the user input and derive desired command from said input.
Help
Description:
Help represents the help command that is called by any user.
JoinedNewGuild
Description:
The JoinedNewGuild class defines the event for when the bot joins a new guild.
Kick
Description:
Kick represents the kick command that is called by a user with admin privileges.
LeftGuild
Description:
The LeftGuild class defines the event for when the bot leaves a guild.
Lines
Description:
Lines represents the lines command that is called by any user.
MemberJoinedGuild
Description:
The MemberJoinedGuild class defines the event for when someone joins a guild that the bot resides in.
MemberLeftGuild
Description:
The MemberLeftGuild class defines the event for when someone is removed from a guild, whether by choice or by force.
MemberPanel
Description:
The MemberPanel class is responsible for generating the list of members associated for each guild.
Shutdown
Description:
Shutdown represents the shutdown command that is called by the admin.
Silence
Description:
Silence represents the silence command that is called by an admin.
Unban
Description:
Unban represents the unban command that is called by an admin.
